# Design Token System (REQUIRED)

You MUST use ONLY these design tokens:

```css
--background: 220 13% 8%;      /* Dark theme base */
--foreground: 220 8% 95%;      /* Primary text */
--card: 220 8% 15%;           /* Card backgrounds */
--border: 220 13% 25%;        /* Borders and dividers */
--primary: 220 8% 40%;        /* Primary actions */
--muted: 220 8% 9%;          /* Muted backgrounds */
```

```typescript
// REQUIRED: Design tokens only
<div className="bg-background text-foreground border-border">

// FORBIDDEN: Custom colors
<div style={{ backgroundColor: '#123456' }}>
<div className="bg-[#123456]">
```

## Typography Scale (MANDATORY)

You MUST use ONLY these classes:
- `text-xs` (12px) - Helper text, captions
- `text-sm` (14px) - Body text, labels
- `text-base` (16px) - Default body
- `text-lg` (18px) - Subheadings
- `text-xl` (20px) - Page headings
- `text-2xl` (24px) - Section titles
- `text-3xl` (30px) - Main headings